Name: Tory
Message: Hah, I may have ;)  Someone picks a card and then reads out a word - there are different categories like dates or movie titles. And whatever they read out everyone has to write down a made up definition for... Like if it's a date you make up something that happened that day, or if it's a movie title you make up a plot description. The person who picks the card writes down the real answer and mixes them in with the fake ones, then they read them all out and everyone has to guess what the real answer is.
